      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>A holographic strike sign consists of a small projection unit attached to a dowel; it displays a holographic image or message programmed by the user. A holographic strike sign grants its holder a +2 circumstance bonus to Intimidate checks to bully individuals attempting to move past them. If used as an improvised weapon, a holographic strike sign deals an extra 1 point of electricity damage on a critical hit but then breaks.</p>\n<p>A holographic strike sign requires one hand to hold, but two to wield as an improvised weapon. It uses a battery and consumes 2 charges per hour of use.</p>"
